{"tid":763283,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"男人之間既打量，一定係睇體重","createTime":"2018-08-01T03:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T05:19:27.000Z","uid":123335,"like":11,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a25771b86e0ccc183834952244bfc87969dd17cb","tid":763283,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:48:02.000Z","msg":"每當你見到個陌生男人<br />\n會好自然打量一下<br />\n會心中暗地裡計算大家既膊鬥實力<br />\n點解？ 純粹係男人既天性<br />\n<br />\n而強弱既指標<br />\n一定係睇體重<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，入廁所見到個陌生男人<br />\n你170cm , 70kg 有肌肉<br />\n你面對186cm , 60kg 瘦底<br />\n你會完全覺得對方冇料到，冇壓力<br />\n<br />\n反而，你170cm, 55kg 瘦底 <br />\n對方186cm , 60kg 瘦底<br />\n你會感到有壓力，會感到自己既弱小<br />\n<br />\n真人真事，前排170cm 既我由58kg bulk到去73kg <br />\n我個178cm , keep住65kg 既fd 見到我bulk後話我大隻左 strong 左後反而會覺得我高左<br />\n<br />\n所以話<br />\n男人之間既硬實力<br />\n一定係睇體重 睇mass<br />\n你越大mass 就越屈機"},{"pid":"e14a0de1b22af5a0e5039a61bc6a789070670f18","tid":763283,"uid":130901,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"好重要<br />\n決定邊個做0邊個做1"},{"pid":"0821a6de62c5eb17a800499873889c5023a4dbef","tid":763283,"uid":5649,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"不嬲睇賓州硬度，去廁所一見到大碌就含落去<br />\n睇下夠唔夠硬"},{"pid":"7f5ba944e0def0eece04d35654f2f53f239ac3bd","tid":763283,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:50:54.000Z","msg":"呢個亦係點解連登仔睇唔起曹星如<br />\n覺得自己有能力打撚死曹星如<br />\n<br />\n男人之間既打量<br />\n你mass 細就代表弱<br />\n冇人會服你"},{"pid":"9706f98c3c2bc54f5b43786f9b53ddf2c09a6714","tid":763283,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:51:00.000Z","msg":"170<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e6d337dade5897668f178291d98e8f3c058c45","tid":763283,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:52:07.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n165 <br />\n80kg<br />\n啲人見到我都怕怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />